    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The non-living bodies of animals, and sometimes of humans, with an emphasis on the structure of the body rather than death or corruption. With butchers, it refers the whole trunk of a slaughtered animal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
